title: Israel arrested 19 Palestinians in West Bank
text: Home Page Global Middle East Israel arrested 19 Palestinians in West Bank last updated: Oct 25,2024 Israel arrested 19 Palestinians in West Bank + - Ramallah - Israeli occupation forces arrested 19 Palestinians Thursday in a wide-scale campaign of raids and incursions in various areas in the occupied West Bank, Palestinian Prisoners Club (PPC) announced.اضافة اعلان The raids saw confrontations in some areas and extremist Jewish settlers also attacked olive pickers in the city of Jenin. In its statement, the PPC said armed clashes erupted after the Israeli army stormed Balata and Askar al-Jadid camps in Nablus.
